creator: Gmamba Studio Games
descriptionHtml:
Slingshot Race Arena is a 3D game based on the physics of a slingshot where you have to compete with your racing rivals for a place on the platform.
Control the car by moving your finger across the screen. Knock your racing rivals out of the arena to be the last one standing. Don't let the difficulties scare you - have fun, race with your enemies and become the coolest rider in the arena!
descriptionShort: Take part in arena races. Shoot enemies like a slingshot
